{
  "stem": "3085.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And as I say, the SS, they were panicking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And at some point, just a few days prior to the-- our liberation, we were taken to-- they were all-- we were all being collected and taken to-- to Auschwitz proper from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And as I understand it, the plan was to have us all machine gunned somewhere in between, taken out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And at some point, there were supposed to be some other SS waiting for us with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But it turns out that they were gone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "The Russians were so close, they were just gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So we just marched into Auschwitz proper, the Auschwitz camp, from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we stayed there a couple of days, or maybe a few days, until the Russians arrived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we didn't know whether we were going to be liberated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we actually expected not to survive it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the-- the common wisdom was that those who stay in the camp are going to be exterminated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "About a couple of weeks before, they organized transports, and the ones who felt they were-- they actually gave you the choice.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you wanted to, you could-- you could march with a group of people and be-- you know, a forced march to-- towards Germany, towards-- away from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of the-- some of the older twins actually decided to go with that transport.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Obviously, we weren't in any kind of condition, position, to undertake anything like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we stayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you know, they felt, and the common knowledge was-- or opinion was that those who stayed behind haven't got a chance.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As it turned out, a lot of those who did go didn't have a chance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some survived, some didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a terrible forced march.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
